title: Application to 1st Round Counselling Jee Main Mode
content: Is the date to apply for 1st round counselling over? I cant see a definitive date on the site just May 23 as date of jee main rank list announcement

comments.body: Yea i checked this doesnt have closing date for application
If u r selected in the general merit list the clg will contact u wid counseling
Yea but im asking if application for round 1 is still open. If i apply now wud i be considered for round 1 or only for round 2

According to jee mains first attempt, a merit list had come.. Now 23rd final merit for jee mains will come... So if u apply now idt it would be a problem... Ur percentile matters too.. Only then it's worth through mains..
Aight thanks. I have 94.56 perc do u think i have a chance to get cse
Got 94.8 didn't get anything in the first merit list.. I don't wanna hv hopes in the final merit list

That's what they hv messed it up..
